		"description": "<p>You imbue a creature you touch with positive energy to undo a debilitating effect. You can reduce the target's Exhaustion level by one, or end one of the following Effects on the target:</p><ul><li>One effect that Charmed or Petrified the target</li><li>One curse, including the target's Attunement to a cursed magic item</li><li>Any reduction to one of the target's Ability Scores</li><li>One effect reducing the target's hit point maximum</li></ul>",
